FAIL_TO_PASS: when script arg then search for local script-sub.js, .ts, .tsx, .mpjs, .cjs
when name pm and executableDir then spawn local pm-sub.js
when execArgv --inspect then spawn execArgs using port 9230
when construct with name pm and script arg then spawn local pm-sub.js
when name pm and script arg then spawn local pm-sub.js
when name pm and script arg and only script-sub.js then fallback to spawn local script-sub.js
when execArgv --inspect=9240 then spawn execArgs using port 9241
when script arg and absolute executableDir then spawn absolute script-sub.js
when execArgv empty then spawn execArgs empty
when script arg then spawn local script-sub.js
when script arg and relative executableDir then spawn relative script-sub.js
when arguments to executable include option flags then argument order preserved
when script arg is link and and link-sub relative to link target then spawn local link-sub
